# MDZN Partners -- Project Context

## Company

MDZN Partners -- a product and design company building modern, mobile-friendly web experiences.

## Tech Stack

- **Framework**: Next.js (App Router)
- **Language**: TypeScript (strict mode)
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS v4
- **Deployment**: Vercel
- **Design**: Pencil (.pen files) via MCP
- **Testing**: Vitest (unit), Playwright (e2e)
- **Package Manager**: pnpm

## Design Philosophy

- Mobile-first, responsive design
- Accessible by default (WCAG 2.1 AA minimum)
- Performance-conscious (Core Web Vitals targets)
- Clean, modern aesthetic with intentional whitespace

## Directory Conventions

```
src/
  app/          # Next.js App Router pages and layouts
  components/   # Reusable UI components
    ui/         # Primitives (Button, Input, Card, etc.)
    layout/     # Layout components (Header, Footer, Sidebar)
    features/   # Feature-specific compound components
  lib/          # Shared utilities, helpers, constants
  hooks/        # Custom React hooks
  types/        # Shared TypeScript types and interfaces
  styles/       # Global styles and Tailwind config
public/         # Static assets
tests/
  unit/         # Vitest unit tests
  e2e/          # Playwright e2e tests
```

## Naming Conventions

- Components: PascalCase (`UserProfile.tsx`)
- Utilities/hooks: camelCase (`useMediaQuery.ts`, `formatDate.ts`)
- Types: PascalCase with descriptive suffixes (`UserProfileProps`, `ApiResponse`)
- CSS classes: Tailwind utilities; custom classes use kebab-case
- Files: match their default export name

## Git & Branching

- `main` -- production, deployed to Vercel automatically
- `dev` -- integration branch
- Feature branches: `feat/<short-description>`
- Bug fixes: `fix/<short-description>`
- Commit messages: conventional commits (`feat:`, `fix:`, `docs:`, `chore:`, `test:`)
